As local investors have moved to the perceived safety of fixed income products over the past few years, interest-bearing unit trusts have been a big beneficiary. According to the latest Asisa statistics, assets invested in interest-bearing short-term funds have more than doubled from R126.5 billion to R257.6 billion over the past three years. Black Friday SpecialGet 15% discount on our annual subscription!
